Introduction to Full Text Search

Basic usage:
SELECT * FROM posts WHERE to_tsvector('english', title || ' ' || body) @@ to_tsquery('english', 'search & terms');

For performance, add a stored tsvector column with GIN index:
ALTER TABLE posts ADD COLUMN search_vector tsvector;
CREATE INDEX idx_search ON posts USING GIN (search_vector);

Update trigger:
CREATE TRIGGER update_search_vector BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE ON posts
FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION
tsvector_update_trigger(search_vector, 'pg_catalog.english', title, body);

Ranking: ts_rank(search_vector, query) for relevance sorting.
Websearch syntax: websearch_to_tsquery('english', 'user input here') handles quotes and operators.

